  "_comment": "sovereign-os selfdef systemd-journal disk-usage dashboard. Visualizes selfdef_journal_* gauges (selfdef commit ec6a822). Pairs with 5 alerts. Operational-disk observability — pairs with disk-usage dashboard at the journal-subsystem axis.",
  "annotations": {"list": []},
  "editable": true,
